[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1133","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1133.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1495","title":"SuSE Linux xtvscreen 符号链接攻击致任意文件写入漏洞","description":"SuSE Linux 6.0 中的 xtvscreen 程序存在任意文件写入漏洞。本地攻击者可通过符号链接攻击方式，在目标系统上创建指向 pic000.pnm 文件的符号链接，当 xtvscreen 程序运行时将覆盖链接指向的任意文件，导致系统文件被破坏或敏感数据被篡改。该漏洞利用条件为攻击者拥有本地用户权限，危害等级较低，CVSS 评分 2.1。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1495"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:33.817","remediation":"立即升级 SuSE Linux 至 7.0 及以上版本，该版本已修复 xtvscreen 的符号链接竞争条件问题。如无法升级，可移除 xtvscreen 的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/xtvscreen）或直接删除该程序以消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/12580","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/325","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1792"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1133.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0050","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0050.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0405","title":"Linux Lsof 本地缓冲区溢出提权漏洞","description":"Lsof（List Open Files）工具在处理超长命令行参数时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞以 root 权限执行任意代码。受影响系统包括 Debian 2.0、FreeBSD 3.2、OpenBSD 2.4、RedHat 5.2 及 SuSE 6.1 等版本，危害等级高。攻击者需具备目标系统的本地访问权限，即通过本地账号登录后运行特制的 lsof 命令即可触发漏洞，无需额外认证条件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0405"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-02-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:19.623","remediation":"tags. The user asked for the answer to be between <value> and","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/3163","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19374","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0405.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0405","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0405.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0405.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-72r6-cpj9-gh8x/GHSA-72r6-cpj9-gh8x.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--3d8f7267-453f-418a-8f3b-092d47e9d29f.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0050.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1099","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1099.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1405","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16395,\"outputTokens\":34,\"totalTokens\":16429}}","description":"IBM AIX 4.2.1 及之前版本中的 snap 命令存在不安全的临时文件创建漏洞。snap 命令在执行时会在 /tmp 目录下创建 ibmsupt 目录，该目录权限设置为世界可读，且执行 snap -a 时不会清理该目录中的旧文件。本地攻击者可利用此漏洞，通过在 root 用户执行 snap -a 之前预先创建 /tmp/ibmsupt/general/passwd 符号链接或文件，诱使 snap 命令将系统 shadow 密码文件写入攻击者可控的位置，从而导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.2.1 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1405"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-02-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:22.220","remediation":"立即升级到AIX 4.3.2或更高版本，移除/tmp/ibmsupt目录并重新建立，设置权限为600，删除任何恶意创建的passwd文件；如无法立即升级，可在命令执行前临时删除/tmp/ibmsupt目录并创建安全的权限目录为940。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91936783009385&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91954824614013&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/375","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19300","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e358b3016d8b52194aa099dc1255ebe1441bbafa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1405.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1405","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1405.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/94e644a0057439310dc2677c2e4ebd7766be1682/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1405.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/958f1672375e115879b3a6bd13e3638812260c7d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gcvv-4h27-hqp8/GHSA-gcvv-4h27-hqp8.json","https://github.com/lcashdol/advisories/blob/32733f854e018593b94f048e59ce3442a76d2767/advisory-9.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1405.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/375/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a32a8be3-115e-4d1a-b931-1ab3b612dbd1.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1099.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0913","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0913.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1060","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9067,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":10751}}","description":"Tetrix TetriNet 守护进程 1.13.16 版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该漏洞源于程序在处理连接主机的 DNS 主机名时未对长度进行有效校验，当远程攻击者从一个具有超长 DNS 主机名的主机连接到目标系统的 31457 端口时，即可触发缓冲区溢出，导致守护进程崩溃产生拒绝服务，并可能进一步执行任意命令。攻击者无需身份认证，只需能够访问目标端口并控制其反向解析主机名即可实施攻击。该漏洞 CVSS v2 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1060"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-17","updated":"1999-02-17","remediation":"升级 TetriNET 服务端至修复该缓冲区溢出问题的版本（1.13.1 及以上）。若无法立即升级，可在服务端前部署防火墙或代理限制仅信任客户端连接、关闭或过滤 TetriNET 默认 31457 端口的外部访问，并启用资源限制以减少拒绝服务影响。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1060.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1060.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1060","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3d905f6009ce1a0cb55b6b90198454d955586615/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1060.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1060.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3xr9-56qc-vgpf/GHSA-3xr9-56qc-vgpf.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1060.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6a35e01f-9c82-4365-a727-7af8d726e1c6.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0913.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0913.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0042","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0042.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0396","title":"NetBSD/OpenBSD TCP服务器 select/accept 竞争条件拒绝服务漏洞","description":"NetBSD和OpenBSD系统的TCP服务器在处理select()和accept()系统调用时存在竞争条件漏洞。远程攻击者可以利用该竞争条件，在特定时间窗口内发送精心构造的网络请求，导致服务器进程进入死锁状态或崩溃，从而造成拒绝服务。攻击条件较为苛刻，需要精确的时间控制，攻击复杂度较高。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0396"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-17","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"OpenBSD用户应应用errata 002补丁或升级至OpenBSD 2.4及以上版本；NetBSD用户应升级至1999年2月8日之后的内核版本。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙层面限制对TCP服务的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0396","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0396","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/af5cedcf472f3690d94c4249ff35246f15692534/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0396.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6hqw-w28m-789c/GHSA-6hqw-w28m-789c.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0042.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1003","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1003.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1180","title":"O'Reilly WebSite 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"O'Reilly WebSite 1.1e 及 Website Pro 2.0 存在命令注入漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向 args.cmd 或 args.bat 脚本的参数中注入 shell 元字符（如 `|`、`;`、`` ` `` 等），以 Web 服务器进程权限在目标系统上执行任意系统命令。该漏洞允许攻击者完全控制受影响服务器，可能导致数据泄露、植入后门或横向移动。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1180"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:53.360","remediation":"升级 O'Reilly WebSite 至 2.1 以上版本。该产品已停止维护，建议迁移至 IIS 或 Apache 等现代 Web 服务器，并在应用层严格过滤输入中的 shell 元字符（如 | & ; $ `）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://oliver.efri.hr/~crv/security/bugs/NT/buffer.html","http://www.tryc.on.ca/archives/bugtraq/1999_1/0612.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1180.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1180","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1180.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1180.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/args_bat.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q697-gcxw-q87j/GHSA-q697-gcxw-q87j.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88632/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1180.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000527.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/A/args_bat.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1003.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1003.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1003.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0026","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0026.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0374","title":"Debian GNU/Linux cfengine 符号链接攻击漏洞","description":"Debian GNU/Linux 发行版中的 cfengine 软件包存在符号链接攻击漏洞。cfengine 是一款基于主机的配置管理工具，通常以 root 权限运行。由于其在处理临时文件时未充分验证符号链接的真实性，拥有本地账户权限的攻击者可通过在可写目录中创建恶意符号链接（指向 /etc/shadow 等系统关键文件），诱导 cfengine 以 root 权限错误地读取或覆写目标文件，导致敏感信息泄露或系统完整性破坏。该漏洞利用条件为攻击者需具备本地 shell 访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0374"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.563","remediation":"建议升级 cfengine 至 1.5.4 及以上版本，该版本修复了临时文件创建中的符号链接跟随漏洞。使用 cfengine 管理文件时避免将临时文件写入公共可写目录（如 /tmp），或使用专属临时目录并设置 umask 077 限制访问权限。在 Debian 系统中及时应用 apt-get update && apt-get upgrade 保持软件包更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0374"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0026.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0027","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0027.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0375","title":"Network Flight Recorder webd 缓冲区溢出代码执行漏洞","description":"Network Flight Recorder (NFR) 2.0.2-Research 版本的 webd 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份验证即可通过网络向 webd 服务发送特制请求，触发缓冲区溢出，从而在目标系统上以服务进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，可导致机密性、完整性和可用性完全受损。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0375"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-16","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"NFR 2.0.2-Research 已停止维护，建议升级到厂商后续安全版本或迁移至替代网络监控方案。如无法升级，应在网络边界防火墙限制对 webd 服务端口的访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0375","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0375"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0027.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1027","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1027.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1260","title":"Hughes Technologies mSQL 服务端敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"mSQL (Mini SQL) 2.0.6 存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向服务器发送 ServerStats 查询请求，获取当前登录用户列表、数据库名称及服务器版本号等敏感信息。该漏洞源于对查询接口未实施有效的访问控制，未经身份认证即可触发，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。攻击者可利用泄露的信息进一步探测系统缺陷，为后续渗透攻击提供依据。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1260"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:03.557","remediation":"将 mSQL 升级至 3.x 最新版本以修复信息泄露问题，或在防火墙层面限制对 mSQL 服务端口（默认 1114/tcp）的非信任来源访问。长远建议迁移至仍受维护的数据库系统（如 MySQL 或 PostgreSQL），并关闭不必要的远程连接功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91910115718150&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1777","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1260.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1260","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1260.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1260.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7fw7-4m2q-jp4c/GHSA-7fw7-4m2q-jp4c.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87764/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1260.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/0b7b3d855cd8fca7b800fb29d6754e2da82897b6/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1027.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0311","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0311.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0714","title":"Compaq Tru64 UNIX edauth 命令漏洞","description":"Compaq Tru64 UNIX 操作系统的 edauth 命令存在权限管理缺陷，本地攻击者无需额外认证即可利用该命令读取系统上的敏感文件，导致机密信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Compaq Tru64 UNIX 多个版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0714"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1999-02-15","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"Compaq（现 HP）已针对 Tru64 UNIX 的 edauth 命令漏洞发布安全补丁，建议用户联系厂商获取对应操作系统版本的补丁程序，或升级到已修复该漏洞的 Tru64 UNIX 版本。由于该产品已停止主流支持，建议迁移至受支持的替代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0714","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0714"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0311.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0043","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0043.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0404","title":"SmartMax MailMax 1.0 SMTP 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SmartMax MailMax 1.0 的 SMTP 服务组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 25 端口发送特制的超长 SMTP 命令触发该漏洞，导致目标系统拒绝服务或执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台下的 MailMax 1.0 版本，无需身份认证即可利用，危害等级高。厂商未提供官方补丁，建议停止使用该软件或通过防火墙限制 SMTP 端口的访问。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0404"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-02-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:19.490","remediation":"升级 SmartMax MailMax 至 2.0 或更高版本。该产品已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的邮件服务器软件，并在防火墙中限制 SMTP 端口（25/TCP）仅允许可信来源访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0404","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20600","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0404.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0404","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0404.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0404.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/310.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/mailmax_imap_overflows.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0404.json","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/snort/drop-rules/exploit.rules","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0043.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1393","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1393.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1203","title":"Ascend Multilink PPP for ISDN 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Ascend Multilink PPP for ISDN 4.6 及早期版本在处理多链路 PPP 端点标识符时存在验证缺陷，远程攻击者可通过发送伪造的端点标识符数据包，触发协议栈异常导致拨号连接中断，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Ascend ISDN 接入设备 4.6 及之前版本，攻击者无需认证即可从远程发起攻击，利用方式为发送伪造的 PPP 端点标识符数据包，导致目标设备拨号连接中断或服务不可用，CVSS 评分 5.0，属中危拒绝服务漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1203"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:56.330","remediation":"建议将 Ascend 路由器/接入设备的软件版本升级到 4.6 或更高版本（Ascend 官方已在该版本中修复 Multilink PPP 对伪造 Endpoint Identifier 的处理逻辑，可防止 ISDN 拨号远程拒绝服务）。如暂时无法升级，可在接入侧启用对 PPP 对等端 Endpoint Identifier 的合法性校验，并配置 ACL 限制仅允许受信任的 ISDN 拨号用户对端地址发起 Multilink 连接，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91868964203769&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91888117502765&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7498.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1203.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1203","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1203.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d281505551869bb381f43b6d1c6cb3abf45ad885/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1203.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/424512debdca84cc53ffa1fb3810a74f7b1905a5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-563j-86xg-r8f7/GHSA-563j-86xg-r8f7.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88923/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1203.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/7fda9011502d7fc255ac49660ff374bd64965608/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1393.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0612","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0612.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0372","title":"Microsoft BackOffice Server 4.0 安装程序敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft BackOffice Server 4.0 安装程序在安装 SQL Server、Exchange Server 或 Microsoft Transaction Server 时，会要求用户输入相关服务账户名和密码，并将这些凭据以明文形式写入 <systemdrive>\\Program Files\\Microsoft Backoffice\\Reboot.ini 文件中。安装完成后（无论成功与否），该文件未被自动删除。本地攻击者若能登录服务器，即可读取该文件获取明文账户密码，进而利用获取的凭据提升权限或访问受保护资源。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0372"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-02-12","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装完成后手动删除 <systemdrive>\\Program Files\\Microsoft Backoffice\\Reboot.ini 文件，该文件仅由安装程序创建，删除后不会自动重建。建议在每次 BackOffice Server 4.0 安装完成后（无论成功与否）立即删除此文件，防止本地攻击者读取明文账户密码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ217004","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-005"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0612.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0611","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0611.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0371","title":"Lynx lynx 本地符号链接敏感文件覆盖漏洞","description":"Lynx 文本浏览器在处理临时文件时存在不安全的符号链接跟踪漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在 /tmp 目录下预创建指向目标敏感文件的符号链接，诱导 Lynx 将临时数据写入该链接指向的文件，从而覆盖系统关键文件，导致数据破坏或权限提升。利用条件为攻击者拥有本地账户权限且 Lynx 以当前用户权限运行。该漏洞影响早期版本 Lynx，CVSS 评分 1.2，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":1.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0371"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.167","remediation":"升级 Lynx 至 2.7.1 或更高版本，该版本已改用 mkstemp() 安全创建临时文件，避免预测 /tmp 路径导致的竞争条件。如无法升级，确保 /tmp 目录设置粘滞位（chmod 1777 /tmp），并通过设置环境变量 TMPDIR 指向用户私有临时目录来缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0371"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0611.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1259","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1259.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1375","title":"Microsoft IIS 3.0/4.0 showfile.asp 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 和 4.0 自带的 showfile.asp 活动服务器页面使用 FileSystemObject（FSO）组件读取文件，但未对传入的 file 参数进行有效过滤与校验。远程攻击者无需身份认证，即可通过构造包含目标文件路径的 file 参数向 showfile.asp 发送 HTTP 请求，越权读取服务器上的任意文件，包括配置文件与敏感文档，造成严重的信息泄露。该漏洞影响所有部署并启用 showfile.asp 的 IIS 3.0/4.0 站点，攻击条件仅为可访问该页面并发送特制请求。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1375"],"sources":["exploitdb","cve"],"published":"1999-02-11","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"删除或重命名存在缺陷的 showfile.asp 页面，禁止匿名访问调用 FileSystemObject 的 ASP 脚本；在 IIS 服务管理器中移除或注销 scrrun.dll 的脚本执行权限以禁用 FSO 组件，并将站点迁移至 IIS 5.0 及以上版本，同时配置 NTFS 权限限制 IUSR 账户仅可读取必要文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91877455626320&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/230","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19194"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19194"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1259.toml"}]